    <h3 id="decide-point">How to decide point after members voted?</h3>
    <p>After flipped the cards after members voted, there'll a list of colorful point bars in <b>Action</b> section. As moderator, you're able to choose point, by clicking on the corresponding point bar. If put mouse on the point bar, there'll be "check icon" <img src="data:image/png;base64," /> on the bar, indicating it's selectable. See screenshot: <%= image_tag "decide-point.png", width: "100%" %></p>
    <h3 id="start-room">How to start a grooming session?</h3>
    <p>Click the <a href="/rooms/new" target="_blank"><b>Create room link</b></a> on right top in the navigation bar.</p>
    <h3 id="edit-room">How to edit a grooming session?</h3>
    <p>After created the room, you're able to see an <b>Edit button</b>, just click it to edit the room. See screenshot: <%= image_tag "edit-room.jpg", width: "100%" %></p>
    <h3 id="sort-room">How to sort/re-order tickets/stories?</h3>
    <p>Go to <b>Edit page</b> or the room, under the <b>Stories</b> section, put mouse on <b style="color:blue">↕</b>, you'll see your pointer ️become "move" icon. Drag on the icon to re-oreder the tickets. See screenshot: <%= image_tag "room-sort.jpg", width: "100%" %></p>
    <h3 id="voted-results">How to see voted ticket results?</h3>
    <p>Click on <b>Finished</b> tab under <b>Stories</b> tab, see screenshot: <%= image_tag "finished-tickets.jpg", width: "100%" %>. BTW, by clicking icon <i class="fa fa-refresh"></i>, you can re-vote for this ticket.</p>
    <h3 id="skip-ticket">Can I skip ticket?</h3>
    <p>Yes. First, you'll need to flip the cards, then there'll be a <b>Skip</b> button in the <b>Action</b> section. See screenshot: <%= image_tag "skip-ticket.jpg", width: "100%" %></p>
    <h3 id="clear-votes">Can I clear the votes and revote for current ticket again?</h3>
    <p>Yes. First, you'll need to flip the cards, then there'll be a <b>Clear votes</b> button in the <b>Action</b> section. See screenshot: <%= image_tag "clear-votes.jpg", width: "100%" %></p>
    <h3 id="kick-people">How to kick people out from a room?</h3>
    <p>Click "<i class="fa fa-edit"></i>Edit" in <b>People</b> section, then click ❌ to remove peole. Then click "<i clas="fa fa-check"></i> Complete", all done! See screenshots: <%= image_tag "kick-01.jpg", width: "100%" %><%= image_tag "kick-02.jpg", width: "100%" %></p>
    <h3 id="technology">What technology does Pokrex rely on?</h3>
    <p>
      <ul>
        <li>Rails</li>
        <li>ActionCable</li>
        <li>ReactJS</li>
        <li>PostgreSQL</li>
        <li>Bootstrap</li>
        <li>FontAwesome</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <h3 id="feedback">How can I give feedback?</h3>
    <p>
      You can send feedback using one of the following methods:
      <ul>
        <li>Click "Blue chat icon" to talk to me at bottom right.</li>
        <li>If you're a GitHub user: Post an issue at <a href="https://github.com/hlcfan/pokr/issues" target="_blank">https://github.com/hlcfan/pokr/issues</a></li>
      </ul>
    </p>
